    <description>Typed multi-agent orchestration for .NET — capability-based sandboxing, railway-oriented pipelines, circuit breakers, and immutable audit trails. Build secure, composable AI agent systems with compile-time guarantees.</description>
    <releaseNotes>v1.0.0: Initial release — IAgent typed contract, AgentContext with capability sandboxing, AgentCapability flags, sequential and parallel pipelines, CircuitBreaker, AgentOrchestrator, AuditTrail.</releaseNotes>
    <tags>ai agents orchestration multi-agent capability-security railway-oriented-programming result circuit-breaker pipeline monadic</tags>
    <repository type="git" url="https://github.com/Danny4897/MonadicSharp.Agents" />
